From: Cursor Agent <cursoragent@cursor.com>
Date: Tue, 7 Jul 2026 09:19:06 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Fix wallet persistence and integrate modular chain registry

- Enable Wagmi reconnectOnMount so wallet stays connected after refresh
- Add Phase 1 chain registry (8 mainnets + BlockDAG experimental; testnets in dev)
- Wire wagmi/viem chains from registry instead of Ethereum + Base only
- Add network picker on Assets page with chain switch controls
- Show loading state while wagmi reconnects on Assets and Overview
- Copy chain icons and add networks i18n keys across all locales
